<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM6.9">
<l>maṅkala nalvaṉa mālaimārvi lilaṅka mayiṟṟaḻaip pīlicūṭip</l>
<l>poṅkiḷa vāṭai yaraiyiṟcāttip pūṅkottuk kātiṟ puṇarappeytu</l>
<l>koṅku naṟuṅkuḻa lārkaḷōṭu kuḻaintu kuḻaliṉi tūtivantāy</l>
<l>eṅkaḷuk kēyoru nāḷvantūta vuṉkuḻa liṉṉicai pōtarātē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Wearing a feather from the peacock tail,</l>
<l>putting on a bright, soft garment around the waist,</l>
<l>placing flower bunches so that they are attached to the ears,</l>
<l rend="indent">as the auspicious, beautiful forest garland shone on [Your] chest,</l>
<l>You came sweetly blowing the flute with the women with curly hair that smells of honey,</l>
<l rend="indent">embracing [them].</l>
<l>As You come blowing [the flute] one day, it is us that the music of Your flute will not reach.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
